{"type":"message","id":"f2fd8b18","parentId":"ddd66987","timestamp":"2026-03-25T14:20:30.906Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Need to recall from memory? Probably command is `clawhub install <skill-name>` or `clawhub add <skill>`. I'll answer based on typical.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]在 `clawhub` 中把一个 Skill 安装到本地的基本命令格式是：\n\n```bash\nclawhub install <skill-name>\n```\n\n或者使用完整的 GitHub 地址：\n\n```bash\nclawhub install https://github.com/your‑org/your‑skill-repo\n```\n\n执行后 `clawhub` 会把对应的 Skill 拉取到 `~/.openclaw/extensions/` 目录下并自动生成必要的 `openclaw.plugin.json`，随后你就可以在 `openclaw skill run <skill-name> …` 中直接调用它。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":18764,"output":212,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18976,"cost":{"input":-18764,"output":-212,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-18976}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774448418665}}
